      "financial_text": "The company reported total revenue of 4.2 million USD for the fiscal year ending December 2023. Revenue is derived from three primary income sources: SaaS subscription fees (2.8M USD), professional services (0.9M USD), and hardware sales (0.5M USD). Operating expenses totalled 3.8 million USD, resulting in an operating income of 0.4 million USD. Asset information: fixed assets (property and equipment) are recorded at 1.6 million USD net of depreciation. Current assets include cash and cash equivalents of 1.1 million USD, trade receivables of 0.7 million USD, and inventory valued at 0.3 million USD. Total assets stand at 3.7 million USD. Liability details: total liabilities were 2.3 million USD, comprising a long-term bank loan of 1.5 million USD secured against fixed assets, trade payables of 0.5 million USD, and accrued expenses of 0.3 million USD. No dividend was declared during the period. The auditor noted a going concern qualification in the accompanying notes. Retained earnings declined by twelve percent compared to the prior year. Net cash flow from operations was positive at 0.2 million USD for the reporting period.",
